Preconditions:
The method should take three integer parameters: `n`, `delay`, and `forget`.
The value of `n` should be a positive integer.
The value of `delay` should be a non-negative integer.
The value of `forget` should be a non-negative integer.
The method should return an integer value.

Postconditions:
The method should return the number of people who know the secret at the end of day `n`.
The returned value should be modulo `10^9 + 7`.